TextEng: Farewell.
Marcus? Was he a mage, perhaps? Kept a Journal?
Text: 마르쿠스? 혹시 마법사였나? 일지를 갖고 있었어?

TextEng: He's probably dead in the streets.
Ha! He's dead! I saw his corpse under a dozen zombies!
Text: 하! 그는 죽었어! 수십 마리 좀비 밑에 깔린 시체를 봤다고!

TextEng: I am sorry, but he fell to zombies. I found his body.
I found his possessions. I could give them to you.
Text: 그의 유품을 찾았어. 당신에게 줄 수 있어.

TextEng: Actually, I was mistaken. I don't have his things.
Text: 실은 착각했어. 그의 물건은 내게 없어.

TextEng: He had this staff. Take it.
He had a journal. Take it.
I don't have anything else of his.
Heh, I have his things now. Let's talk price.
Text: 헤, 이제 그의 물건은 내가 갖고 있어. 값을 치러.

TextEng: I wish I could help.
Then live in denial, fool. I told you what I saw.
Text: 그럼 부정하며 살아. 바보야. 내가 본 걸 말해줬잖아.

TextEng: I'm sure he will turn up.
Powerful? Maybe I should seek him out.
I have not seen anyone by that name.
Me no see no Marcus anywheres.
Brother dead, probably.
This Marcus, he maybe write stuff? Was he spell-chucker?
Text: 이 마르쿠스, 혹시 뭐 쓰는 사람? 마법 쓰는 사람이었어?

TextEng: Bye byes. Me go.
Maybe me find powerful guy. Maybe me get stuff.
Text: 나 힘센 사람 찾을지도. 그럼 전리품도 얻지.

TextEng: He be here sometime. No worry.
Text: 그 언젠가 여기 올 거야. 걱정 마.

TextEng: Me not want to say but... him dead.
He so dead! Weak and stupid and dead!
You be fool. Me say what is true.
Me wish could help yous, but can't.
I have dead Marcus stuff. Maybe you... pay for it?
Text: 나 죽은 마르쿠스 물건 있어. 혹시... 돈 줄래?

TextEng: Me have dead Marcus stuff. Maybe give to you?
Text: 나 죽은 마르쿠스 물건 있어. 너한테 줄까?

TextEng: Him have book he write. Take it.
Text: 그 사람 쓴 책 가져. 여기.

TextEng: Him have big staff. Here, you take.
Heh... whoopsies. Me not have anything.
Me not have nothing more.
Farewell.
Go bye.
What are you waiting for?
What you wait for heres?
You just did. Out with it. What do you want?
Text: 방금 그랬잖아. 자, 말해. 뭘 원하는데?

TextEng: You did anyways. What you want, already?
Tell me of your brother.
You tells me about your brother.
Have you seen many survivors, or just zombies?
You see lotta survivors, or just dead guys?
Text: 너 생존자 많이 봤어, 아니면 죽은 놈들만 봤어?

TextEng: Is this the only safe place he might have gone?
Text: 그가 갔을 만한 안전한 곳이 여기뿐인가?

TextEng: This the only safe place he maybe be?
<StartAction>(Hold up staff)</Start> You know staff? Me finds it on his body.
Text: <StartAction>(지팡이를 들어 보인다)</Start> 이 지팡이 알아? 나 그 사람 시신에서 찾았어.

TextEng: <StartAction>(Hold up staff)</Start> Do you recognize this staff? I found it on his body.
Text: <StartAction>(지팡이를 들어 보인다)</Start> 이 지팡이 알아봐? 그의 시신에서 찾았어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> <StartAction>(Hold up Journal)</Start> Me find body of his. Look, his book he write.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> <StartAction>(일지를 들어 보인다)</Start> 나 그 사람 시신 찾았어. 봐, 그 사람이 쓴 책.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> <StartAction>(Hold up Journal)</Start> I found his body. Look, I found his journal.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> <StartAction>(일지를 들어 보인다)</Start> 그의 시신을 찾았어. 봐, 일지를 찾았어.

TextEng: Me gots staff stick. Yous gonna have to pay lots.
Text: 나 지팡이 막대기 있어. 너 많이 돈 내야 해.

TextEng: I have his staff. You will pay well for it, I think.
Text: 그의 지팡이가 있어. 당신은 비싸게 값을 치를 거야.

TextEng: You gots to pay more. Gimmie.
Text: 너 돈 더 내야 해. 내놔.

TextEng: That's not enough. I demand more.
That okay. You take staff.
Text: 나 더 많이 돈 받을 거야.

TextEng: That will do nicely. Take the staff.
Me gots staff he had. You just have it. Me give.
Text: 너 이거 가져. 이제 너한테 줄게.

TextEng: I have his staff. You can simply have it.
Me wants pay for book he wroted.
I demand payment for his journal.
No, that not enough.
Text: <StartAction>(일지를 건넨다)</Start> 여기 일지. 그가 쓴 거야.

TextEng: No, that's not enough.
That good. Take dumb book.
That will do nicely. Take the lousy journal.
Then you gets nothing.
Well, then you get nothing.
Me gots book. What me need book for? You just takes it.
I have his journal. I will give it to you.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No, there nothing else me find.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No, there was nothing else that I found.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me see him dead. Honest. You believe because it true.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I swear to you, I saw his body. You will have to accept my word.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No, there nothing. Me sorry.
<StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No, I'm sorry. There was nothing.
Me got's nothing more to says to you.
I have nothing more to say to you.
